'''热带风暴克劳德特'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Claudette}}）是[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]第三场获得命名的风暴，也是这年第一个袭击美国的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统于8月16日经[[东风波|东风波]]和上层[[低气压|低气压区]]发展而成，然后在[[塔拉赫西|塔拉赫西]]以南近海强化成热带风暴。当天下午，气旋已达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]95公里的最高强度并稳步逼近[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]西北狭长地带。8月17日清晨，克劳德特的中心[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]佛罗里达州[[圣罗莎岛_(佛罗里达州)|圣罗莎岛]]。风暴登陆数小时后就减弱成热带低气压，预警职责移交[[美国天气预报中心|水文气象预报中心]]。8月17日晚，气象机构发布有关克劳德特的最后一份公告，宣布气旋在[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]上空消散。

[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]向佛罗里达州沿海地区发布热带风暴警告，建议多个县中生活在[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]易发区域的居民及时撤离。[[巴拿马城_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马城]]近海因海况恶劣导致一人丧生。当天贝县近海还有一人从船上落水后淹死。风暴在[[开普科勒尔_(佛罗里达州)|开普科勒尔]]催生出一场{{lang|en|[[改良藤田级数|EF-0]]}}级[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，致使11幢民居受损，损失数额约为10万3000美元（2009年美元）。此外，佛罗里达州的海滩及沿海物业还因气旋受到价值12万5000美元（2009年美元）的破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Claudette 2009 track.png}}
热带风暴克劳德特源于8月7日离开非洲西海岸的一股[[东风波|东风波]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | date = 2010-01-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011222/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL042009_Claudette.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Storm Claudette Tropical Cyclone Report | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | format = PDF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL042009_Claudette.pdf }}</ref>。8月11日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始监控行进至[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东约965公里海域的东风波。系统向西移动，[[对流|对流]]活动杂乱无章，气象机构预计系统短时间内不会有进一步发展。<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927053335/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908110532/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908110532 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908110532/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908110532 | archivedate = 2012-09-27 }}</ref>截至8月12日下午，东风波关联的对流活动仍然很少<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-12 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927054941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908121147/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908121147 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908121147/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908121147 }}</ref>。系统继续在东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]行进，但因外界大气环境存在强烈的上层[[风切变|风切变]]而难以重新组织<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-12 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090830152751/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908122331/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908122331 | archivedate = 2009-08-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908122331/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908122331 }}</ref>。

8月15日，东风波从[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]上空经过，在此期间对流已开始围绕中心聚拢<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-15 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927055605/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908151742/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908151742 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908151742/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908151742 }}</ref>。次日清晨，系统快速组织，在抵达佛罗里达州[[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]西南方向约130公里洋面时逐渐发展出下层环流。美国国家飓风中心预计，由于外界环境利好，系统会在当天发展成热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author1 = James Franklin | author2 = Robbie Berg | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305035324/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908160545/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908160545 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908160545/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908160545 }}</ref>。数小时后，该机构发布针对[[2009年大西洋飓风季|飓风季]]第四号热带低气压的首份公告。由于风切变少，气旋得以快速发展，气象部门预计低气压会在12小时内达到热带风暴标准。气旋围绕东侧的[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]边缘向西北方向移动。<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304213342/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.001.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Depression Four Discussion One | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.001.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。位于[[塔拉赫西|塔拉赫西]]的{{lang|en|[[NEXRAD|NEXRAD]]}}（意为“新一代雷达”）[[多普勒雷达|多普勒气象雷达]]发现系统环流中心周围风速达到每小时65公里，美国国家飓风中心因此于[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]上午11点将其升级成热带风暴，并以“克劳德特”（{{lang|en|Claudette}}）命名<ref>{{cite report | author1 = David Roberts | author2 = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Storm Claudette Tropical Cyclone Update | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.update.08161613.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224144/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.update.08161613.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

8月16日下午，[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]上空的[[低压槽|低压槽]]令风暴所在海域的风切变出现小幅增长，环流中心因此从对流中暴露出来<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Michael Brennan | author2 = David Roberts | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Storm Claudette Discussion Four | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304215524/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.004.shtml }}</ref>。但即便是在这样的情况下，克劳德特还是在此期间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]95公里的最高强度<ref name="TCR" />。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月17日早上5点10分，气旋以风速每小时85公里强度从圣罗莎岛最东端附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。此后不久，系统[[气压|气压]]降至1005[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.68[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最低值。<ref name="TCR" />登陆数小时后，风暴关联的对流快速消退<ref>{{cite report | author = Dan Brown | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220838/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Storm Claudette Discussion Six | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.discus.006.shtml? }}</ref>，到了{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点，美国国家飓风中心发布针对克劳德特的最后一份公告，宣布气旋降级成热带低气压，水文气象预报中心至此开始接手监控和预警职责<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Michael Brennan | author2 = David Roberts | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Depression Claudette Public Advisory Six-A | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193747/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.public_a.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.public_a.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月17日晚，水文气象预报中心发布有关克劳德特的最后一份公告，宣布气旋残留在[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]上空消散<ref name="TCR" />。系统残留接下来又持续存在数小时，最终于8月18日在[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]上空失去踪影<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:TS_Claudette_2009_1715_UTC_August_16.jpg|thumb]]
热带低气压形成之际，美国国家飓风中心向[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]和[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]边界到[[萨旺尼河|萨旺尼河]]（{{lang|en|Suwanee River}}）河口间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Depression Four Public Advisory One | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222539/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.public.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al04/al042009.public.001.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。有关部门敦促相对地区居民尽快检查应对飓风所需要的工具包，做好防灾准备<ref>{{cite news |author=Melissa Nelson |publisher=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Tropical Storm Claudette forms off the Fla. Coast |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4m4ZsPg?url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gVWjsPEiqe1tEu2mhBIRaxxGi8owD9A444301 |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gVWjsPEiqe1tEu2mhBIRaxxGi8owD9A444301 }}</ref>。位于克劳德特中心以东的佛罗里达州西部沿海地区居民收到警告，风暴可能产生暴雨并引发洪灾<ref>{{cite news |author=Associated Press |newspaper=''St. Petersburg Times'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Tropical Storm Claudette churns off Florida's gulf coast; storm warnings along Panhandle, Big Bend |archivedate=2009-08-16 |url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/weather/hurricanes/tropical-storm-claudette-churns-off-floridas-gulf-coast-storm-warnings/1028050 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4i11Ihh?url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/weather/hurricanes/tropical-storm-claudette-churns-off-floridas-gulf-coast-storm-warnings/1028050 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。新闻报导中预计风暴登陆点附近的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]会有0.9至1.5米高<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=CBS4 |date=2009-08-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4iel8sZ?url=http://cbs4.com/hurricanes/tropical.depression.four.2.1130525.html |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=TD #4 Upgraded To Tropical Storm Claudette |url=http://cbs4.com/hurricanes/tropical.depression.four.2.1130525.html |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[沃库拉县|沃库拉县]]应急管理办公室呼吁风暴潮易发地区的居民赶在克劳德特来袭前撤离<ref>{{cite news |author=Scott L. Nelson |newspaper=''Wakulla News'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2016-03-05 |title=Coastal Flooding Expected in Wakulla County from Tropical Storm Claudette |archivedate=2016-03-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002646/http://www.wakulla.com/Wakulla_News/Local_News/Coastal_Flooding_Expected_in_Wakulla_County_fromTropical_Storm_Claudette_200908168414/ |url=http://www.wakulla.com/Wakulla_News/Local_News/Coastal_Flooding_Expected_in_Wakulla_County_fromTropical_Storm_Claudette_200908168414/ }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}夜间7点过后不久，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻阿拉巴马州[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]办事处向佛罗里达州[[德斯坦_(佛罗里达州)|德斯坦]]到密西西比州[[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]之间区域发布热带风暴强度大风警告<ref>{{cite report |author=National Weather Service in Mobile, Alabama |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Hurricane Center |location=Miami, FL |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Hurricane Local Statement for ANA |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/text/WTUS84-KMOB.shtml |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4xtmuIH?url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/text/WTUS84-KMOB.shtml |archivedate=2009-08-16 }}</ref>。气象部门预计克劳德特会产生超过180毫米雨量，佛罗里达州西北狭长地带大部分区域因此收到洪灾观察预警<ref>{{cite news |author=National Weather Service in Tallahassee, Florida |publisher=Weather Underground |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Areal Flood Watch |url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/FL/016.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4xp5zu4?url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/FL/016.html |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。阿拉巴马州东南部大部分地区收到内陆热带风暴警告<ref>{{cite news |author=National Weather Service |publisher=Weather Underground |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Inland Tropical Storm Warning |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/AL/060.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4yE9qd5?url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/AL/060.html }}</ref>。

8月16日下午，政府部门向佛罗里达州[[湾县_(佛罗里达州)|湾县]]圣布拉斯海角的圣约瑟夫半岛州立公园和斯通州立公园居民发布强制疏散令<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=WMBB13 |date=2009-08-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4w17WEY?url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_gulf_county/mbb779339/ |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Severe Weather — Gulf County |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_gulf_county/mbb779339/ |archivedate=2009-08-16 }}</ref>。[[贝县_(佛罗里达州)|贝县]]开设有两间避难所，其中一间位于迪恩·博兹曼高中，另一间在博兹曼学习中心。生活在沿海低洼地区的居民也收到自愿撤离令。<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=WMBB13 |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Severe Weather — Bay County |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_bay_county/mbb779335/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4wC5eQR?url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_bay_county/mbb779335/ }}</ref>[[华盛顿县_(佛罗里达州)|华盛顿县]]虽然没有开设避难所的计划，但该县紧急行动中心还是把待命级别上调到二级<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=WMBB13 |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4wW9ywO?url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_washington_county/mbb779344/ |title=Severe Weather — Washington County |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_washington_county/mbb779344/ }}</ref>。[[富兰克林县_(佛罗里达州)|富兰克林县]]紧急行动中心进入三级待命，并向[[鳄鱼角|鳄鱼角]]（{{lang|en|Alligator Point}}）发布自愿疏散令<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=WMBB13 |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j4wjl6Kz?url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_franklin_county/9338/ |title=Severe Weather — Franklin County |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.panhandleparade.com/index.php/mbb/article/severe_weather_franklin_county/9338/ }}</ref>。下午得知风暴最新动向后，[[沃尔顿县_(佛罗里达州)|沃尔顿县]]官员宣布该县进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |newspaper=''Chipley Bugle'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Local state of emergency declared |url=http://www.chipleybugle.com/news/?p=1719 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j528p8lZ?url=http://www.chipleybugle.com/news/?p=1719 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2009-08-16 }}</ref>。[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]还在沃库拉县[[克劳福德维尔_(佛罗里达州)|克劳福德维尔]]的一所教堂开设避难所<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |newspaper=''Tallahassee Democrat'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |title=Updated: Crawfordville church open to those seeking shelter from Tropical Storm Claudette |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j58gn4tb?url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816006/Updated++Crawfordville+church+open+to+those+seeking+shelter+from+Tropical+Storm+Claudette+ |archivedate=2009-08-16 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816006/Updated++Crawfordville+church+open+to+those+seeking+shelter+from+Tropical+Storm+Claudette+ }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==

=== 佛罗里达州 ===
[[File:Claudette_2009_rainfall.png|thumb]]
截至8月16日晚，富兰克林县部分地区已降下43毫米以上雨量<ref>{{cite news |author=Local Resident of Franklin County, Florida |publisher=Weather Underground |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2013-01-05 |title=Daily Summary for August 16, 2009: White City, Franklin County, Florida |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130105093712/http://www.wunderground.com/weatherstation/WXDailyHistory.asp?ID=KFLWHITE1&month=8&day=16&year=2009 |archivedate=2013-01-05 |url=http://www.wunderground.com/weatherstation/WXDailyHistory.asp?ID=KFLWHITE1&month=8&day=16&year=2009 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]在8月16日共降下91毫米雨量，打破1931年时创下的单日降雨量纪录<ref>{{cite web |author=National Weather Service |publisher=Weather Underground |date=2009-08-17 |accessdate=2009-08-17 |title=Record Report |url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/AL/065.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j6Fmea4A?url=http://www.wunderground.com/US/AL/065.html |archivedate=2009-08-17 }}</ref>。但是，除有一棵树倒在[[98号美国国道|98号美国国道]]上外，气旋没有对阿巴拉契科拉造成其它破坏<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Report |newspaper=''Tallahassee Democrat'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-20 |title=Update: Tropical Storm Claudette headed west of Panama City |url=http://www.tallahassee.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816002 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2009-08-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820160231/http://www.tallahassee.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20090816%2FBREAKINGNEWS%2F90816002 }}</ref>。截至克劳德特消散时，[[大卡普皮特礁|大卡普皮特礁]]（{{lang|en|Big Coppitt Key}}）的最高降雨量已达143毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | date = 2009-08-19 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Tropical Storm Claudette rainfall map | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025228/http://origin.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/claudette2009filledrainblk.gif | url = http://origin.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/claudette2009filledrainblk.gif }}</ref>。

据报导，[[开普科勒尔_(佛罗里达州)|开普科勒尔]]附近出现[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，风暴[[雨带|雨带]]令佛罗里达州多地收到龙卷风警告<ref name="spcreports1">{{cite news | url = http://www.spc.noaa.gov/climo/reports/090816_rpts.html | title = 090816's Storm Report | date = 2009-08-16 | work = NOAA | publisher = Storm Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184720/http://www.spc.noaa.gov/climo/reports/090816_rpts.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref name="WBBH">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210327/http://www.nbc-2.com/global/story.asp?s=10938329 | url = http://www.nbc-2.com/global/story.asp?s=10938329 | title = Tornado touches down in Cape Coral | date = 2009-08-16 | publisher = WBBH — NBC2 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 }}</ref>。开普科勒尔有23户民宅因龙卷风受损<ref>{{cite news |author=Chris Umpierre |newspaper=''The News-Press'' |date=2009-08-17 |accessdate=2009-08-17 |title=Cape tornado: Resident describes near miss |url=http://www.news-press.com/article/20090817/NEWS0101/908170353/1075 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j6byirUA?url=http://www.news-press.com/article/20090817/NEWS0101/908170353/1075 |archivedate=2009-08-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，其中11套的损失数额就有约10万3000美元<ref>{{cite news |author=Connor Holmes |newspaper=''Cape-Coral-Daily-Breeze'' |date=2009-08-17 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |title=Tornado damages 23 homes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j6bnnx8V?url=http://www.cape-coral-daily-breeze.com/page/content.detail/id/509351.html?nav=5011 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.cape-coral-daily-breeze.com/page/content.detail/id/509351.html?nav=5011 |archivedate=2009-08-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Heather L. Ryan |publisher=Justice News Flash |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |title=Tornado strikes Fort Myers area |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j8HEHhVr?url=http://www.justicenewsflash.com/2009/08/18/tornado-strikes-fort-myers-area_200908181914.html |url=http://www.justicenewsflash.com/2009/08/18/tornado-strikes-fort-myers-area_200908181914.html |archivedate=2009-08-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。佛罗里达州[[佛罗里达州州长名单|州长]][[查理·克瑞斯特|查理·克瑞斯特]]曾短暂视察受龙卷风破坏的地点<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.naplesnews.com/news/2009/aug/17/gov-touts-benefits-charter-schools-during-fort-mye/ | title = Gov. touts benefits of charter schools during Fort Myers stop | last = Williams | first = Leslie | date = 2009-08-17 | work = Naplesnews | publisher = Scripps Interactive Newspapers Group | accessdate = 2012-02-22 | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120222045905/http://www.naplesnews.com/news/2009/aug/17/gov-touts-benefits-charter-schools-during-fort-mye/ }}</ref>。经之后确认，这场龙卷风的风速为每小时110至120公里，在[[改良藤田级数|改良藤田级数]]中属{{lang|en|EF}}-0级<ref name="NWSTornado" /><ref>{{cite news |author=JL Watson |publisher=''News-Press'' |date=2009-08-18 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-08-18 |title=Governor Crist views Cape Coral tornado damage |archivedate=2009-08-18 |url=http://www.news-press.com/article/20090818/NEWS0101/908180352/1075 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j8B1lUpM?url=http://www.news-press.com/article/20090818/NEWS0101/908180352/1075 }}</ref>。美国国家气象局表示，这场龙卷风于{{lang|en|UTC}}20点42分至20点45分在地面行进约560米<ref name="NWSTornado">{{cite news | author = Dan Noah | publisher = National Weather Service in Tampa Bay, Florida | date = 2009-08-19 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Cape Coral Tornado on August 16, 2009 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/images/tbw/TopNews/PDF/TornadoCapeCoral16aug2009.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181151/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/images/tbw/TopNews/PDF/TornadoCapeCoral16aug2009.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

另据报导，佛罗里达州[[巴拿马城_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马城]]近海有一人淹死<ref>{{cite news | last = Murray | first = Bill | publisher = [[美国广播公司|ABC]] | work = Channel 33/40 | date = 2009-08-16 | accessdate = 2016-05-01 | title = Drowning Reported in Panama City | url = http://www.alabamawx.com/?p=21869 | archivedate = 2016-03-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160328232647/http://www.alabamawx.com/?p=21869 }}</ref>。受树木倒塌及电缆中断的影响，截至8月16日晚，有关部门已将20号公路约1600米路段封闭。[[莱昂县_(佛罗里达州)|莱昂县]]共有440户居民家中停电。<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |newspaper=''Tallahassee Democrat'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-17 |title=Updated: Highway 20 lone road closure in Big Bend area; report outages, road closures |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j5BOf4bX?url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816024/Updated++Highway+20+lone+road+closure+in+Big+Bend+area++report+outages++road+closures |archivedate=2009-08-17 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816024/Updated++Highway+20+lone+road+closure+in+Big+Bend+area++report+outages++road+closures }}</ref>到{{lang|en|UTC}}次日凌晨1点40分时，这截公路已重新开放，全部440户居民家中的电力供应均已恢复<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |newspaper=''Tallahassee Democrat'' |date=2009-08-16 |accessdate=2009-08-17 |title=Updated: Highway 20 reopened; report outages, road closures |url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816024/Updated++Highway+20+reopened+++report+outages++road+closures |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j5KPtdc3?url=http://www.tallahassee.com/article/20090816/BREAKINGNEWS/90816024/Updated++Highway+20+reopened+++report+outages++road+closures |archivedate=2009-08-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[帕克_(佛罗里达州)|帕克]]附近及巴拿马城市中心都有停电情况<ref name="News Herald poweroutages">{{cite news | url = http://www.newsherald.com/news/open-76666-blog-panama.html | title = TS Claudette 9:20 p.m.: Power back on in downtown P.C. (with photos) | date = 2009-08-16 | publisher = News Herald | accessdate = 2012-02-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120226100353/http://www.newsherald.com/news/open-76666-blog-panama.html | archivedate = 2012-02-26 }}</ref>。沃尔顿县也有约500居民失去供电<ref>{{cite news |author=Debbie Wheeler |publisher=''The Walton Sun'' |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2010-06-26 |title=Claudette does little damage |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j8DT4IwT?url=http://www.waltonsun.com/news/claudette-3402-damage-little.html |url=http://www.waltonsun.com/news/claudette-3402-damage-little.html |archivedate=2009-08-18 }}</ref>。

[[奥卡鲁沙县|奥卡鲁沙县]]有1267位居民在风暴期间失去供电，其中大部分在数小时内恢复，但由于持续性的风害影响，该县各地都出现零星停电情况，最多时同时有500户家庭受到影响<ref>{{cite news | author = Sean Flynn | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100124050849/http://www.nwfdailynews.com/news/county-19777-claudette-okaloosa.html | newspaper = ''Northwest Florida Daily News'' | date = 2009-08-17 | accessdate = 2010-01-24 | title = Okaloosa County weathers Claudette; no injuries reported | url = http://www.nwfdailynews.com/news/county-19777-claudette-okaloosa.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2010-01-24 }}</ref>。全县各地因气旋引发的洪灾共计蒙受价值约2万5000美元损失<ref name="NCDC">{{cite journal | volume = 51 | number = 8 | title = Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena with Late Reports and Corrections | date = 2009-08 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2016-04-22 | deadurl = yes | issn = 0039-1972 | editor1 = Joseph E. Kraft | archivedate = 2016-04-22 | editor2 = Rhonda Herndon | format = PDF | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-0D959391-5093-4B2F-8912-68B86531DA6D.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422133454/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-4484D0F4-DF9F-4DC9-976D-608CB30FEA29.pdf | journal =  }}[http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html 此网站] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html |date=20160414065723 }}可查询美国国家海洋和大气管理局风暴数据平面出版物的内容，但查询结果链接有效时间仅有24小时，用户可选择“2009-08”获得所需要的信息。</ref>。贝县近海有一人从船上落水，救援人员虽然一度将他救起，但他之后又从救生援上掉落并失踪，搜救工作又持续一段时间后取消，预计该男子已经死亡<ref>{{cite news |author=Don Germaise |publisher=ABC Action News |date=2009-08-17 |accessdate=2009-08-17 |archivedate=2009-08-17 |deadurl=yes |title=Claudette claims 1st fatality |url=http://www.abcactionnews.com/news/local/story/Claudette-claims-1st-fatality/-qoVMa58y0KE2fyE9NSLxg.cspx |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j66nfoBZ?url=http://www.abcactionnews.com/news/local/story/Claudette-claims-1st-fatality/-qoVMa58y0KE2fyE9NSLxg.cspx }}</ref>。

[[File:Tropical_Depression_Claudette_2009-08-17_1915Z.jpg|thumb]]

贝县、沃尔顿县、富兰克林县和湾县沿海地区因克劳德特产生的海浪导致约9.1至12.2米深的沙子流失，估计这4个县流失的沙子总价值为10万美元<ref name="NCDC" />。风暴登陆期间以[[德斯坦_(佛罗里达州)|德斯坦]]所测风暴潮最高，约为0.7米<ref name="NCDC" />。佛罗里达州共有两人遇难，损失数额约为22万8000美元<ref name="NCDC" />。

=== 其它地区 ===
风暴登陆期间，阿拉巴马州南部多地因暴雨威胁而收到山洪爆发观察预警<ref>{{cite report | author = Marybeth Gerhardt | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | date = 2009-08-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502011418/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/2009/CLAUDETTE/CLAUDETTE_07.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/2009/CLAUDETTE/CLAUDETTE_07.html | archivedate = 2016-05-02 | title = Tropical Depression Claudette Advisory Seven }}</ref>。受气旋影响，该州大范围地区有中等程度降水，最高降雨量有54毫米<ref name="ADV9">{{cite report | author1 = Brendon Rubin-Oster | author2 = Frank James Pereira | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502011754/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/2009/CLAUDETTE/CLAUDETTE_09.html | author3 = Robert Oravec | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | date = 2009-08-18 | accessdate = 2016-05-02 | title = Tropical Depression Claudette Public Advisory Nine (Final) | archivedate = 2016-05-02 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/2009/CLAUDETTE/CLAUDETTE_09.html }}</ref>。局部地区仅两小时就降下51毫米雨量，促使美国国家气象局发布山洪爆发警告<ref>{{cite news |author=Dennis Sherer |newspaper=''Times Daily'' |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2009-08-18 |title=Tropical storm fizzles in north Alabama |url=http://www.timesdaily.com/article/20090818/NEWS/908189984/1011/NEWS?Title=Tropical-storm-fizzles-in-north-Alabama |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j8Gb2Qwb?url=http://www.timesdaily.com/article/20090818/NEWS/908189984/1011/NEWS?Title=Tropical-storm-fizzles-in-north-Alabama |archivedate=2009-08-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，[[黑尔县_(阿拉巴马州)|黑尔县]]、[[萨姆特县_(阿拉巴马州)|萨姆特县]]和[[佩里县_(阿拉巴马州)|佩里县]]则收到山洪爆发观察预警<ref>{{cite news | author = Stephanie Taylor | newspaper = ''Tuscaloosa News'' | date = 2009-08-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-02 | title = Tropical Storm Claudette moves into West Alabama | archivedate = 2009-08-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090822205039/http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20090817/news/908179993?Title=Tropical-Storm-Claudette-moves-into-West-Alabama | publisher = Gatehouse Media | url = http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20090817/NEWS/908179993?Title=Tropical-Storm-Claudette-moves-into-West-Alabama }}</ref>。克劳德特的残留令阿拉巴马州部分地区的空气变得非常潮湿，当地在多个下午出现[[雷暴|雷暴]]天气。部分雷暴还伴随着强烈阵风，并以[[杰佛逊县_(阿拉巴马州)|杰佛逊县]]所测阵风时速最高，有75公里。<ref name="NCDC" />[[彩虹市_(阿拉巴马州)|彩虹市]]有幢公寓楼被[[闪电|闪电]]击中并引发火灾，楼内两个单元的住户因此疏散，估计这场火灾一共造成价值两万美元的破坏<ref name="NCDC" />。风暴的外围雨带还在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]产生降水，降雨量最高的[[班宁堡|班宁堡]]达到60毫米<ref name="ADV9" />。

